title: TWO TOP BANANAS -- with Don Rickles, Don Adams, Carol Wayne
description:
This early Showtime special from 1982 is a parody of burlesque and vaudeville,
done in both early and late 20th century stylings.  The two Dons who worked together in "Get Smart!" years earlier : Adams and Rickles are the hosts, who appear in sketches. Also in the cast are Rhonda Shear (who posted this on her 
You Tube channel where I got it from) and Murray Langston.
